      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available for acquisition is a 2008 Porsche Cayman S, an exceptional example of mid-engine engineering. This chassis is powered by the 3.4L M97 flat-six powerplant, featuring VarioCam Plus for optimized valve timing across the rev range. The power is delivered via a precise 6-speed manual transaxle, offering superior tactile engagement. This unit is equipped with Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM), allowing for variable damping control to mitigate body roll during high-G cornering. Recent preventative maintenance includes a water pump replacement and a borescope inspection of the cylinder bores to confirm the absence of scoring. The hydraulic steering rack provides the communicative feedback synonymous with the 987 platform. While the finish shows minor road patina, the mechanical vitals\u2014including clutch take-up and synchro mesh\u2014remain tight and responsive, ensuring a high-performance driving dynamic.",
