      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a reliable, well-maintained daily driver. The exterior presents beautifully in its original factory finish, showing only minor stone chips on the front fascia consistent with careful highway use. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and has been kept in a smoke-free environment; the leather seats remain supple with only light creasing on the driver\u2019s bolster. All electronic features, including the navigation system, heated seats, and adaptive cruise control, are fully operational. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health. It features a complete service history with oil changes performed every 5,000 miles. Most recently, the brake pads were replaced and the cooling system was flushed to ensure long-term dependability. The engine pulls smoothly, the transmission shifts are crisp, and the suspension remains tight and quiet over bumps. Included are two sets of keys, the original owner's manuals, and a set of all-weather floor mats. This is a turn-key vehicle ready for its next owner to drive home today.",
